---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';

const lang = 'en' as const;
---

<Layout lang={lang}>
  <Header lang={lang} />
  <main class="py-24 lg:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: March 8, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By using Anga Security services (the &quot;Service&quot;), you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, do not use the Service.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">2. Service Description</h2>
        <p>Anga Security is a security audit platform for websites protected by Cloudflare. We offer:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Automated security configuration analysis (Quick Scan, Security Audit).</li>
          <li>Controlled attack simulation against Cloudflare protections.</li>
          <li>Regulatory compliance evaluation.</li>
          <li>Remote security consulting.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">3. User Account</h2>
        <p>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your access credentials. Notify us immediately if you suspect unauthorized use of your account.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">4. Credits and Payments</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Credits are purchased via MercadoPago.</li>
          <li>Credits do not expire and are non-transferable.</li>
          <li>Credits are non-refundable once consumed.</li>
          <li>Prices are in Mexican pesos (MXN) unless otherwise indicated.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">5. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p>You agree to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Use the Service only to analyze domains you own or have explicit authorization to test.</li>
          <li>Not provide Cloudflare API tokens that do not belong to you.</li>
          <li>Not attempt to circumvent Service limitations.</li>
          <li>Not use the Service for illegal activities.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">6. Nature of Reports</h2>
        <p>Reports generated by Anga Security are <strong>advisory</strong> in nature. They do not constitute a formal security audit or compliance certification. Results should be validated by certified professionals before claiming regulatory compliance.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">7. Attack Simulation</h2>
        <p>Attack simulations run exclusively against Cloudflare protection layers (WAF, Bot Management, DDoS Protection). They do not attack origin servers. By requesting a simulation, you confirm that you have authorization to perform security testing on the specified domain.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Anga Security shall not be liable for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Damages arising from decisions made based on reports.</li>
          <li>Service interruptions caused by third parties (Cloudflare, Supabase, MercadoPago).</li>
          <li>Security breaches on analyzed websites.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">9. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>Generated reports are owned by the user who requested them. The platform, source code, algorithms, and the Anga Security brand are the property of ANGA Mexico.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">10. Modifications</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be published on this page and take effect immediately.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">11. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of Mexico. Any disputes shall be resolved in the competent courts of Mexico City.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">12. No Affiliation with Cloudflare</h2>
        <p>Anga Security is an independent service and <strong>is not affiliated with, sponsored by, endorsed by, or certified by Cloudflare, Inc.</strong> Cloudflare{'\u00AE'} is a registered trademark of Cloudflare, Inc. Use of this trademark is solely for descriptive purposes to indicate compatibility of our services. We are not authorized resellers of Cloudflare and have no commercial relationship with Cloudflare, Inc.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">13. Simulation Consent</h2>
        <p>By using the Attack Simulation service, you <strong>explicitly acknowledge and agree</strong> that:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>You authorize Anga Security to execute test payloads (including SQLi, XSS, path traversal and other attack vectors) against your domain.</li>
          <li>These tests are performed through the Cloudflare{'\u00AE'} network and exclusively evaluate Cloudflare protections, not your origin servers.</li>
          <li>You are solely responsible for ensuring you have legal permission to conduct these tests on the specified domain.</li>
          <li>You release Anga Security from any liability arising from the use of simulation payloads against domains for which you lack authorization.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">14. Disclaimer of Warranties (&quot;AS-IS&quot;)</h2>
        <p>The Service is provided <strong>&quot;AS IS&quot; and &quot;AS AVAILABLE&quot;</strong>, without warranties of any kind, express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, accuracy, completeness, or non-infringement. Anga Security does not warrant that:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Reports are error-free or complete.</li>
          <li>The Service will be available without interruption.</li>
          <li>Security recommendations are sufficient to prevent all threats.</li>
          <li>Simulation results accurately reflect production behavior.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">15. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>You agree to <strong>indemnify, defend, and hold harmless</strong> Anga Security, its directors, employees, contractors, and affiliates from and against any claims, demands, damages, losses, costs, liabilities, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising from:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Your use of the Service in violation of these Terms.</li>
          <li>Attack simulations performed against unauthorized domains.</li>
          <li>Use of Cloudflare{'\u00AE'} API Tokens without permission from the account owner.</li>
          <li>Security decisions made based on Anga Security reports.</li>
          <li>Violation of any applicable law or third-party rights.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">16. Contact</h2>
        <p>For inquiries about these terms: <a href="mailto:jose301184@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">jose301184@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer lang={lang} />
</Layout>
